  standards_of_creation = 'PE license (NCEES FE and PE examination completion); Cal. Board of Professional Engineers application; responsible charge documentation per Cal. Bus. & Prof. Code 6703; engineering report and plan stamping requirements per Bus. & Prof. Code 6735.3; NEC compliance documentation; IEEE standards application (power systems, control systems, electronics); professional engineering report format; design calculations and basis of design documentation; construction administration and inspection documentation; Title 24 energy compliance documentation per Cal. Energy Code',
